LEWY CHEMICAL COMPANY, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. ROSETH CORPORATION, Defendant-Appellee. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 10, 1924.) No. 264. Henry J. Lucke, of New York City, for appellant. Munn, Anderson & Munn, of New York City (T. Hart Anderson, of New York City, of counsel), for appellee.

Before HOUGH, MANTON and MAYER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Affirmed, on the opinion of Campbell, District Judge. 290 Fed. 529.
